mrain (0.0.20081228-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix bug at program exit. Add man page
  * Performance update. Add new effect 'Twister'. Minor fixes
  * Performance update. Add support OpenGL 1.5 hardware acceleratiion. Add new option --no-shaders 
  * Add new console options --help and --window-id. GL-logging has been enlarged
  * Fix bugs in Makefile, refactored vertex/fragment shaders and some minor fixes
  * Initial release
  * Fix bugs in build-scripts. Closes: #1.

